@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Reindexar cursos e aulas no search_index
# Observacao: consome OpenAI API para gerar embeddings.
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/reindex

### Busca semantica por texto - Python
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/text-search?q=python

### Busca semantica por texto - Backend
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/text-search?q=quero aprender backend

### Busca semantica por texto - Frontend
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/text-search?q=curso de frontend com react

### Autocomplete
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/autocomplete?q=py

### Busca por voz
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/voice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "quero aprender python"
}

